exercises.name: Flat Barbell Bench Press
exercises.notes: I got 4 out of the 5 sets completed. The last set was a grinder.

exercises.name: Incline Dumbbell Bench Press
exercises.notes: I completed all 4 sets of 12. I might increase the weight next time.

exercises.name: Cable Fly
exercises.notes: I felt an incredible contraction doing these.

exercises.name: Machine Pec Dec
exercises.notes: When I placed my hands higher on the handle bars, I managed to feel a better contraction in my 'inner chest'.

exercises.name: Cable V-Bar Tricep Pushdown
exercises.notes: I got fatigued by the time I got to this exercise. I most likely need to take a break after my main chest movements before starting my tricep movement.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Lateral Raise
exercises.notes: I felt great doing these. I held my hand along the grip of a door, shifted my center of gravity away from the door, and performed the movement perfectly.

exercises.name: Weighted Wide-Grip Pull-ups
exercises.notes: I completed 4 sets of 6, but missed 2 reps on the last set. I'm going to repeat this weight next time.

exercises.name: Barbell Deadlift
exercises.notes: Every set was easy. I felt strong today. Going to increase the weight next time.

exercises.name: Barbell Pronated Bent-Over Row
exercises.notes: I felt like a monster doing these. Will likely use the same weight and aim for slower reps next time.

exercises.name: Hammer Strength High Row
exercises.notes: My favorite back exercise by far. Will increase the weight by 10 next time.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Curl
exercises.notes: I got into the rhythm after the first 2 sets and accidentally did 5 sets... I should probably increase the weight next time.

exercises.name: Hammer Strength Curl
exercises.notes: My favorite bicep exercise by far. It's super fun especially at the end of a pull day.
